

@page
@model ArtWorkStore.Pages.Index1Model
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4">About Art Store</h1>
        <p class="lead">Celebrating Creativity and Passion for Art.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded with a love for the arts, Art Store has grown into a trusted destination for artists and art lovers alike. Our journey began with a small gallery, and today, we are proud to offer a wide range of original artworks, prints, and art supplies to a global audience.</p>
            <p>Our mission is to inspire and nurture creativity in every form. We believe in supporting artists and helping them connect with people who appreciate their work. Every piece we offer is carefully selected to ensure it meets our high standards of quality and creativity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/about-us.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Art Store History" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5 text-center">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <p>At Art Store, we are committed to:</p>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><strong>Creativity:</strong> Fostering an environment where creativity thrives.</li>
            <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Offering only the best in art and art supplies.</li>
            <li><strong>Community:</strong> Building a supportive community for artists and art enthusiasts.</li>
            <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Promoting sustainable practices in the art world.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5 text-center">
        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
        <p>Our team is made up of passionate individuals who are dedicated to bringing you the best in art and creativity. From curators to customer service, every member plays a vital role in our success.</p>
        <a href="/team" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
    </div>
</div>
